{
  "texts": [
    "By using AI algorithms to analyze and learn from user behavior and preferences within XR environments, developers can create more personalized and adaptive XR experiences.",
    "For example, AI can be used to track user gaze and gestures within XR, enabling more natural and intuitive interactions with virtual objects and environments.",
    "Developers can construct more responsive and intelligent Metaverse applications by combining AI and XR, which has a number of advantages for both users and enterprises, including better user experiences, increased productivity, and improved security (Dirk et al. 2021).",
    "Additionally, AI and XR can offer a framework for creating fresh and inventive Metaverse use cases, such virtual healthcare, remote offices, and immersive entertainment.",
    "The goal of XR is to give the user a seamless transition between fully virtual and fully real worlds."
  ]
}